    ('CJUS-P 304', 'PROBATION AND PAROLE', '13508', 'Closed', 'TuTh Tuesday, Thursday 5:30 PM–6:45 PM', 'WB WEB', 'Jennifer Colanese', 0, NULL, 'Lecture', '3', 'WEB-BASED CLASS', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Study of probation, parole, and community corrections as subsystems of criminal justice, including the police, courts, and prisons. Theoretical and historical developments will be considered along with current management and research issues.', ARRAY['COLL (CASE) S&H Breadth of Inquiry credit'], NULL),
