COLL (CASE) A&H Breadth of Inquiry credit
COLL (CASE) Culture Studies: Global Civ & Culture'], NULL),
    ('CLAS-C 205', 'CLASSICAL MYTHOLOGY', '1335', 'Closed', 'TuTh Tuesday, Thursday 2:20 PM–3:35 PM', 'ED 1120', 'Elise Poppen, Yuyuan Zhang', 0, NULL, 'Lecture', '3', 'WENDELL W. WRIGHT EDUCATION BU', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Introduction to Classical Mythology, the myths of Ancient Greece and Rome. Learn about these important societies through the lens of the stories they told about themselves. Discover the influences that resonate throughout literature, art, film, and more to shape modern society.', ARRAY['IUB GenEd A&H credit
