    ('CMLT-C 200', 'HONORS SEMINAR', '13684', 'Closed', 'MW Monday, Wednesday 9:35 AM–10:50 AM', 'WH 104', 'Johannes Turk', 0, NULL, 'Lecture', '3', 'WOODBURN HALL', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'Selected authors and topics, ranging from traditional to modern; for example, Athens and Jerusalem: The Origins of Western Literature. Traditional or current debates and issues of a critical, theoretical, or historical nature. Comparative methodology, interdisciplinary approach.', ARRAY['IUB GenEd A&H credit
